title: 20150413 Person Of Interest Paleyfest Made in New York Panel  Live Stream
author: 李丹
comment:
They are all wonderful.....
 Acker appears shy and much quieter than I'd imagined.
 Caviezel has a much deeper artistic sensibility than I'd Imagined.
 Emerson is always the Intellect with a sense of humor.
Amy Acker is too goddamn cute

This is the most awkward thing I've ever seen...But Amy Acker Is Totally gorgeous
